data.description: Welcome Home! The West Shore!! This adorable Cape style home is just A Hop, skip, a jump to beautiful sandy beaches and the famous Dive Bar!! Nothing to do but move into this Cozy Cape! The home offers 3 bedrooms and a office that can easily be used as a 4th BR. Updated kitchen complete with peninsula, granite counter tops, subway tile backsplash, and SS appliances that are less than two years old! The main level of the home has 2 bedrooms and a full bath, there are Dark Hardwood floors throughout the first floor that were recently installed and refinished. The second floor has another bedroom and an office that can be used as a 4th bedroom. The home is heated with natural gas and has central A/C. A new roof was installed last month, there are solar panels that come with the home but they had to be removed to install the new roof, they will be reinstalled in mid March. There is also a 2 car garage with plenty of room for storage as well as your two autos. Home is being sold As Is, As Is rider will need to be included with your offer, inspections are welcome but for informational purposes only. Close to Marsh Hill Rd exit off of i-95. Easy access to Milford train station. ****The seller is in receipt of multiple offers, the seller is requesting highest and best offers by Monday at Noon.**** ****The seller is in receipt of multiple offers, the seller is requesting highest and best offers by Monday at Noon.**** Agents Please include a As Is Rider with your offers. Solar Agreement has been uploaded to MLS.
